Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的河邊就像是另一個世界似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一直覺得這是個和我無緣的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:19.00,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(280,310)\fad(0,300)}明天去室外活動！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.71,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  心奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向問我們要不要去飯能河原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.17,0:00:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她想讓我們準備點零食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還不知道你明天有沒有空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  那你能來我家一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.10,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話能住一晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我一直想搞一次睡衣派對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個玩偶看上去是不是有些惡趣味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有根頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個漂亮的房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:00:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有考慮準備點蛋糕和餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會難得乾脆去那兒做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些什麼調理的道具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向說會帶可擕式火爐去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.66,0:01:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那法式吐司怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.13,0:01:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是賓館裡會有的那種？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像的要簡單喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.74,0:01:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有雞蛋牛奶和糖就能做了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加點桂皮和蜂蜜的話會很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力醬貌似也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做法式吐司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套道具只要1000円左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是楓同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵肯定會嚇一跳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直不忘小葵的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她太笨拙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得為她做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那是我多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓她能更多更多地展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:06.38,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(125,126)}雞蛋3個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.74,0:02:06.38,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(125,206)}牛奶135cc
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.38,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(125,276)}砂糖75g
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.38,TITLEd,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(125,346)}香草精華少許
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是這樣做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣醃製一晚  接下來只要明天烤一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.42,0:02:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣明天的準備也差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.08,0:02:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做軟軟的雞蛋卷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.94,0:02:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面放點糖會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我非常期待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡軟綿綿的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆的閒聊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  心奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再來過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要道謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是明天肯定會更加…
